<!-- Parish History -->
<section class="mb-5">
  <div class="row g-4 align-items-center">
    <div class="col-md-7">
      <h2 class="h4 fw-bold text-primary-custom">Our History</h2>
      <p>NCC Parish was founded in 1952 by a small group of faithful Catholics who sought to establish a place of worship at the heart of the growing community. From a modest chapel with just 40 families, our parish has grown into a vibrant congregation of over 1,200 registered families.</p>
      <p>Over the decades, we have built our current church building (dedicated in 1978), expanded our school, and launched numerous outreach programs that have made a lasting impact in our neighborhood and beyond.</p>
      <p>Today, NCC Parish stands as a beacon of faith, hope, and charity—rooted in the rich traditions of the Catholic Church while embracing the diverse community around us.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5">
      <div class="rounded-3 overflow-hidden shadow text-center py-5" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);">
        <i class="fas fa-cross fa-5x" style="color: var(--primary); opacity:0.3;"></i>
        <p class="mt-3 text-muted fst-italic">Established 1952</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Mission Statement -->
<section class="bg-primary text-white rounded-3 p-4 mb-5" style="background-color: var(--primary) !important;">
