    <h2 class="h4 fw-bold mb-3">Our Mission</h2>
    <p class="lead mb-0 px-md-5">"To proclaim the Good News of Jesus Christ through worship, education, and service — welcoming all into our parish family and sending them forth to transform the world."</p>
